addr="gt-000S"
title="Separated space">separation</fr:link>. Define a function <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f\colon  X\to \mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex> by
<fr:tex
display="block"><![CDATA[f(x) = \begin {cases}0 & \hbox {if }x\in  U_{1}\\ 1 & \hbox {if }x\in  U_{2}.\end {cases}]]></fr:tex>
Then <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[f]]></fr:tex> is continuous, since for every open subset <fr:tex
display="inline"><![CDATA[A\subseteq \mathbb {R}]]></fr:tex>, the preimage <fr:tex
